    "Additionally, since computations related to the graph structure only occur during propagation, subsequent training for downstream tasks can be performed separately without involving expensive graph operations.",
    "Therefore, arbitrary sequence learning models can be plugged in.",
    "Similarly, SDG [60] employs a dynamic propagation matrix based on personalized PageRank, replacing the static probability transition matrix of APPNP [70].",
    "Specifically, SDG first extracts hidden node features using a model-agnostic neural network.",
    "These features are then multiplied with the dynamic propagation matrix to disseminate neighborhood node information."
